Kuthiwa le ntokazi ibifake intambo kagesi igcwalisa ilahle leselula yayo, ibikhuluma nesihlobo sayo ngesikhathi kwehla lesi sigameko. Umnewabo wale ntokazi uthe bamangele ukuthola ukuthi ubulawe yiselula udadewabo ngoba bamgcine ekhuluma kuyo, bamthola esedindilizile. Uthe bazamile ukumphuthumisa esibhedlela, kwafike kwathiwa usephangalele ngesikhathi efika. Kuthiwa akukacaci ukuthi le selula iqhunyiswe yini njengoba kuyinto engavamile ukwenzeka lena. Abenkampani iHMD ekhiqiza amaselula eNokia, bathe bashaqekile ukuzwa izindaba zokufa komuntu ebulawa yiselula. Bathe bahlala bezibophezele ukuthi bakhe amaselula asezingeni elifanele futhi aphephile kwabangase bawasebenzise. Isidumbu sale ntokazi sigcine sithathiwe siyohlolwa kabanzi ukuthi ngabe yini imbangela yokufa. - The Daily Mail